Xournal++ Static code analyis HOWTO

In this folder are description and manual to run static code analysis on the
Xournal++ project.

Tools which may be used:

== Cppcheck ==
 TODO

== clang ==
To run a scan you execute in the root folder:
 scan-build-3.5 make

After the analysis is finished you can lookt at the results with this command:
 scan-view-3.5 /tmp/scan-build-XXXXXXXXXXXX (replace path)


